ime France.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 31. Jan 2022) 0aArt and societyzFrancexHistoryy20th century. 0aArt and statezFrancexHistoryy20th century. 0aBronzexWar usezFrance. 0aPublic sculpture, Frenchy20th century. 0aWorld War, 1939-1945xDestruction and pillagezFrance. 0aWorld War, 1939-1945xEconomic aspectszFrance. 7aHISTORY / Europe / France.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9780804779715zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780804779715423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780804779715/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles